<![CDATA[<font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">IMPORTANT: DO NOT REPLY on this email. Please read below carefully.</span></b></span></font><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b><br><br><br>RE: Lease # {!Case.Lease__c}</b></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b> - HO {!Case.Account}<br><br></b></span></font><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;">Thank you for contacting SunPower!<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>We are happy to help you through the process&nbsp;of transferring or purchasing your solar lease system as you sell your home.<br><br><b>What are your Options?<br><br></b>When you sell your home, you have two options for handling over your SunPower system to the buyer:<br></span></font><blockquote><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b>Assignment of Lease - </b>You can transfer the lease to the new buyer, and they will continue to pay the lease payments with the same terms you have now.</span></font><br><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"></span></font><br><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b>System Purchase</b> - Alternatively, you can buyout your system, passing your installation to the buyer without additional monthly payments required to SunPower from you or them.</span></font><br><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"></span></font></blockquote><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><br><b>What you can expect:</b> <b>Assignment of the Lease</b></span></font><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><br></font></font><ul><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Once we receive the completed Homesale form, the Buyer will receive an email from SunPower with a credit check/identity verification application (<u>no-reply@credit.sunpowercorp.com</u>)</font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">This application is mandatory and must be completed by the buyer to assume the lease. </font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Once the buyer's credit application is submitted and processed, we will prepare an escrow package (Solar Lease Assignment and Escrow Instructions documents, Financing Statement termination, and Extinguishment of the Notice of the Solar Contract) and mail it to your escrow company. We will deliver the escrow package within 10-14 days from the buyer's credit check approval. <br></font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">All parties will need to sign the </font></font><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Solar Lease Assignment and Escrow Instructions documents at escrow closing and send back to us with the final payment (if applicable) collected by your escrow company.</font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Note that since we do not prorate the monthly lease payments, the escrow package will show the final payment which will include any unpaid months and the full payment for the month your escrow closes.</font></font></li></ul><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b><br></b></span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><b>What you can expect: System Purchase (Lease Buyout)</b></span></font><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><br></font></font></p><ul><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Once we receive the completed HomeSale form, your case manager will provide you with a quote to buyout your system within 3 business days. <br></font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">If you would like to move forward with the purchase, please sign the buyout quote and send back to your case manager so SunPower can prepare an escrow package</font></font><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"> (Purchase Instructions document, Financing Statement termination, and 
Extinguishment of the Notice of the Solar Contract)</font></font> to be emailed to your escrow company.</font></font></li><li><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">All parties will beed to sign the Escrow package at your closing and sent back to us with the payment collected by your escrow company.<br></font></font></li></ul><p><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><b><br></b></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><b>Let's Get Going</b><br></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><br></font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">To get started with either option, please complete the attached form and return it to us via email.</font></font></p><p><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><br></font></font></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><i><b><font size="2"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif">Important Note: Kindly send the requirements on a NEW email and use Homesale Request for </font></font><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;">{!Case.Lease__c} on the subject line.</span></font></b></i></span></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><br></span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;">We appreciate your business and seek to make this transition as smooth as possible so you can focus on getting settled into your new home.</span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><br></span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;">Should you have any concerns or queries feel free to email us at <u>homesale@sunpower.com</u> or call 1-800-321-1770.</span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black;"><br></span></font></p><p><font size="2" face="Arial,Sans-Seri